
<purchabr>BANCO SANTANDER</purchabr> TO BUY WEST GERMANY'S <acqabr>CC-BANK</acqabr>
    MADRID, March 5 - {<purchaser>Banco Santander</purchaser>} signed a <status>letter of
intent</status> with <seller>Bank of America</seller> {<sellercode>BAC</sellercode>} to purchase its <acqloc>West German</acqloc>
affiliate {<acquired>Bankhaus Centrale Credit AG</acquired>}, <acqabr>CC-Bank</acqabr>, the bank said
